  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Oh there you are.


      I was wondering where you had disappeared
      to.'
    nextOption: I didn't disappear.  Thats impossible!
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'It was just a figure of speech.


      Anyway, we have sent word
      to the Sun Temple of your deeds here.


      The High Priestess is expecting
      you.'
    nextOption: Where is the Sun Temple?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Follow the path South out of the camp until you reach the fork.


      Take
      the East path past the pond and into the hills.  You will find the Sun Temple
      high in the mountains.'
    nextOption: Ok. I'll go to the Sun Temple now.
